      "content": "I'm not sure what you mean by \"goblins.\" I need a professional analysis of the actual logistics errors here. Can we stick to the technical possibilities like unit of measure errors, scanning lag, or actual shrinkage? Please give me a serious list of likely causes for these variances.",
